skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: ninety point five
des: Just say: "Alexa, open ninety point five" to tune into 90.5 FM WESA Pittsburgh's NPR News Station. "Alexa pause" or "Alexa stop" will stop the audio. "Alexa resume" will start it up again.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
